<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
     COMMON PROBLEMS
══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-num">04 — Diagnostics</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Common Thermador Problems We Fix</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Thermador appliances fail in predictable ways. Here's what our techs encounter most often — and what's actually causing it.</p>

    <div class="problems-grid">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-title">🔥 Star® Burner Won't Ignite</div>
        <div class="problem-cause">Most often a failed igniter module or cracked igniter cap. Star® burners use a geometry-specific ceramic igniter — generic replacements rarely seat properly, causing intermittent spark failure even when new.</div>
        <span class="problem-tag tag-common">Most Common</span>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-title">🌡️ Oven Temperature Off</div>
        <div class="problem-cause">Usually a failed bake element, worn door gasket allowing heat loss, or a faulty temperature sensor (thermistor). Convection fan failure also creates hot spots. We test all three before ordering parts.</div>
        <span class="problem-tag tag-common">Most Common</span>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-title">❄️ Column Fridge Not Cooling</div>
        <div class="problem-cause">Common culprits: dirty condenser coils (especially in dusty Valley homes), failed thermistor, or compressor starting relay. In coastal homes, salt-air corrosion on condenser components accelerates wear.</div>
        <span class="problem-tag tag-common">Most Common</span>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-title">💧 Steam Oven Not Generating Steam</div>
        <div class="problem-cause">Steam generator scale buildup from LA's hard water is the primary cause — the heating element encrusts over time. A secondary cause is a failed water inlet valve. We descale and test the full steam circuit.</div>
        <span class="problem-tag tag-urgent">Urgent</span>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-title">🍽️ Dishwasher Not Draining</div>
        <div class="problem-cause">Drain pump impeller failure or a blocked drain hose are most common. The Star-Sapphire® auto-open door mechanism adds a secondary failure point — a motor or latch issue can prevent the cycle from completing.</div>
        <span class="problem-tag tag-common">Most Common</span>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-title">🔆 Warming Drawer Not Heating</div>
        <div class="problem-cause">Heating element failure is the most common cause. Because warming drawers run at lower temperatures for longer periods, elements fail differently than oven elements — gradual degradation rather than sudden failure.</div>
        <span class="problem-tag tag-common">Most Common</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

